snippet.title: Boxy Trial Beta 0.3 - Release Trailer | Desx
snippet.description:
New in Boxy Trial Beta 0.3:

-Particles! (˘︶˘).｡*♡
-Improvements to the UI
-You can access the Options Menu from the levels through the Pause Menu
-Improvements to the levels
-Level Transitions
-Death Particles
-Fixed Checkpoints

Hope you enjoy playing!



__________________________________________________________________



Available on Windows, Mac and Android
Get it for free:


Itch.io: https://desx.itch.io/boxytrial
Google Play: Coming soon...
